<p>A lot of inspiration for this living collection comes from [Michelle Barker](https://css-irl.info), who wrote about upcoming browser features on [Smashing Magazine](https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2022/03/new-css-features-2022/) and on [CSS { In Real Life }](https://css-irl.info/exciting-times-for-browsers-and-css/).</p>

<p>Please feel free to [suggest new features](https://github.com/{{ author.github }}/{{ site.repository }}/tree/main/src/data/browserFeatures.json) or even [other browsers](https://github.com/{{ author.github }}/{{ site.repository }}/tree/main/src/data/browsersByType.json).</p>

{% for feature in browserFeaturesSorted %}
	<section class=" [ owl--medium ] ">
		<h2 id="{{ feature.id }}">{{ feature.title | safe }}{% if feature.language %} <small>({{ feature.language | capitalizeFormat }})</small>{% endif %}</h2>
		{{ feature.description | markdownFormat | safe }}
		<ul>
			{% for link in feature.links %}
				<li>{{ link | markdownFormat | safe }}</li>
			{% endfor %}
		</ul>
		{% caniuse feature.id %}
	</section>
{% endfor %}
